<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA40">
<l>curukkāka vāṅkic culāviniṉ ṟaiyār</l>
<l>nerukkāmuṉ ṉīrniṉaimiṉ kaṇṭīr – tiruppolinta</l>
<l>vākattāṉ pāta maṟintu maṟiyāta</l>
<l>pōkattā lillai poruḷ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As a shortcut, dragging, moving around, standing, without first</l>
<l>nearing doubt-filled people, you think, see:</l>
<l>there is no sense in enjoyment that does not know,</l>
<l>although it knows, the feet of him on whose chest Śrī is flourishing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
